{
  "id": "adv_main_02_05_05",
  "title": "東京編1章25話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyo-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "バンプロとの契約、レギュラーの仕事も確認した所\n特に問題はありませんでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I went over their contract with Van Productions and their recurring gigs.\nI didn’t find any issues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 6.93333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、これがウチの契約書だ\nまず、簡単に説明すると……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ here’s our contract.\nFirst‚ I’ll give you a simple explanation…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 12.3666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、サインしたよ\nこれでいい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There. All signed.\nThat okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.533333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 14.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、ちゃんと中身を読んでくれ\n凄く大事なものなんだぞ。ご両親の同意だって必要だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-whoa there… You should read it properly.\nIt’s an important decision‚ and you’ll need parental consent.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.63333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "さっき、最後まで目を通したけど\n何も問題はないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I went over the whole thing earlier‚\nand I couldn’t find any issues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.499999999999993,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 27.1666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 30.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "神崎せんぱい、なめられちゃいますよ～\nバンプロよりギャランティが安いと思いまーす",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio senpai‚ you’ve got to play hard to get!\nLooks like our salaries will be lower than at Van Productions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.86666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さすがにバンプロほどには……\n出来るだけ頑張った金額ではあるんだが、すまない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ yes‚ we’re not as big as Van Productions.\nWe try to compensate you as fairly as we can… Sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.83333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 42.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "私はこれでいいです。甲とか乙とか書かれても\nどっちのことだか分からなくなります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m fine with this. I can’t make heads or tails\nof which party is which in this thing anyway!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.89999999999999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 48.2333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "まったく貴方達は……私はLizNoirが\n自分達らしく歌える場所を用意してくれればそれでいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You girls…. As long as LizNoir\nhas a place where we can sing and be ourselves‚ we’ll be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.066666666666656,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 55.8666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "まさか君は僕達の個性を\n潰すような仕事はさせないよね？　僕は信じてるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re not going to make us do work that stifles\nour creativity‚ will you? I trust you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.533333333333324,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 63.2333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……その言い方、圧を感じるんだが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ thanks for the additional pressure…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.23333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 66.5666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "葵さんがそんなこと言うなんて……！\nきっと凄い方なんですね！　私も信じます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ if Aoi-san says she trusts you…\n…then you must be a wonderful person! I trust you‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 73.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "私も信じてますよ～売れなくなってもキワドイ水着を\n着せてグラビア出演を強要するなんて思ってません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I trust you‚ toooo. Even if we fail to bring in money‚\nI trust you won’t make us do gravure photoshoots in skimpy swimsuits.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.43333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 83.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、どうしてもと言うなら\n一番年長の莉央さんが出るべきですよね～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you insist‚\nthen that’s a job for Rio-san since she’s the oldest!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 86.9666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "なっ……！？\nそんなの私だってお断りよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What?!\nHey‚ I’d refuse to do that‚ too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 90.6666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、だいぶ前\n莉央はグラビアやらなかったっけ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ Rio‚\ndidn’t you do a gravure photoshoot a while ago?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "あれは元々姫野さんが勝手に取って来て\n強引にやらされちゃったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ but Himeno-san got that gig for me without my permission.\nI was forced into it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.13333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 99.2333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "こほん、俺はどんな仕事でも内容を正確に伝える\n君達の意思を尊重するよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A-hem. I promise to honestly tell you what it entails no matter the gig.\nI’ll respect your wishes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルは事務所の道具じゃない\nむしろアイドルが事務所を利用して輝いてくれればいい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Idols are not pawns at our agency.\nIf anything‚ an agency should be a tool for idols to make themselves shine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 112.666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "Ai",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-ai003.m4a",
      "text": "うわああ～～っ！　感動しました！\n私、こんなに大切にしてもらったの初めてです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wowww! I’m moved to tears!\nI’ve never been cherished like this before!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 120.333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "甘い言葉でだますのが、芸能界の常套手段って\n知ってますけど、とりあえず信用しときま～す",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that deception through flattery is a well-known convention of showbiz‚\nbut I’ll trust you for now!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 128.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "こころ、貴方\n目上の人に対しての言葉遣いというものをね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kokoro‚ you need to learn a thing or two\nabout speaking politely to your superiors.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.76666666666668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05/sud_vo_adv_main_02_05_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "構わないよ。そもそも、俺は本当の代表じゃない\n三枝さんが戻ってくるまでの繋ぎなんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don’t mind. After all‚ I’m only the acting president.\nI’m just doing this until Saegusa-san gets back.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 141.633333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
